node.title: Guys starts fight with murse @dcwalthall on the train over COVID

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Anesthesia on August 09, 2021. May be a meme of 1 person and text that says 'How smart you feel when you take boards GASSY.CRNA'.

node.text: The smartest day of your life. Then it’s all downhill after you leave that exam room. 6 months later you’re wondering how you even graduated. Make sure you have the @vargo_anesthesia_ app to fill in all your knowledge gaps.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Anesthesia on August 09, 2021 tagging @pass_dat_gas. May be an image of 3 people, people standing and text that says 'Pass dat gas GASSY.CRNA Surgeon: How do I use this again? Scrub tech Rep: it's all in the hips'.

node.text: “I want you to give up that laparoscopic bullshit, and focus on robots.” Collab with @pass_dat_gas

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Anesthesia on August 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Tell me you're a surgeon, but not a really good one Jeep IM-GOD TR GASSY.CRNA'.

node.text: Ego of a plastic surgeon, but the skills of family practice drs rounding in icu
